<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<em>The opaque midnight folds, inset with a multitude of tiny diamonds, of this cloak swirl around you and you feel a hint, a fragment of the knowledge and power to restore that lay in Luthien, the most beautiful being that even knew death.</em> <p>
The Shadow Cloak of Luthien ([6, +20]) is an <a href="./Artifact">Artifact</a> that is the goal of the <a href="./SpecialLevel">SpecialLevel</a> <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Spoilers_2fDungeons_2fTheCrypt"><img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">The Crypt</a>, found on level 70 of <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Spoilers_2fDungeons_2fAngband"><img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">Angband</a>. As far as dependable artifacts go, this is one of the easier if you know what you are doing to obtain, and quite useful for most people. 
</p>
<p>
It can be activated for restore life levels every 450 turns. 
</p>
<p>
It can store a spell. 
</p>
<p>
It increases your intelligence, wisdom, charisma, stealth, luck and speed by 2. 
</p>
<p>
It makes you invisible. 
</p>
<p>
It provides resistance to acid, fire and cold. 
</p>
<p>
It provides a random high resistance. 
</p>
